# Nomad Fits – Men's Clothing eCommerce Website

## Project Overview

Nomad Fits is an eCommerce website designed for modern, stylish men who value adventure, travel, and versatility in fashion. The website offers high-quality, travel-friendly clothing that combines comfort, functionality, and contemporary style. Whether navigating urban environments or exploring the outdoors, Nomad Fits provides fashion solutions that adapt to every lifestyle.

This project serves as a real-world portfolio piece, demonstrating how to build a fully functional online store using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and data from the Platzi Fake Store API.

---

## Features

- Display products dynamically from an API
- Responsive product cards
- Product search functionality
- Add-to-cart counter
- Modern and clean user interface
- Mobile-friendly design
- Hero section and company information
- Real-time product filtering

---

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6)
- Fetch API
- Platzi Fake Store API